      "index": 0,
      "text": "read file \u0027config.json\u0027, write to %cfg%",
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "A read of config.json lands the file as {item, json} (born-native: a json payload of\nunknown shape is \u0060item\u0060). The critical lazy invariant: stamping \u0060type=item\u0060 does NOT\nparse \u2014 \u0060%cfg%\u0060 untouched is still the raw json *string*. Materialisation only fires on\nnavigation (see ReadConfigJson_NavigateMaterialisesField). Requires the config.json\nfixture committed alongside.",
